<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/24028977">美国是否写不出《三国演义》这样的书？如果是，为什么？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1793371" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">看了个很火热的题<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/21101845?q=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%86%99%E4%B8%8D%E5%87%BA%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E6%BC%94%E4%B9%89%E3%80%8B%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%EF%BC%9F" class="internal">中国是否拍不出《权力的游戏》这样的作品？如果是，为什么？</a><br>所以，大家也来答一下这个吧~~~~</div>


</div>
