<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="378">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$aaa-ssss-88" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/aaa-ssss-88" class="zg-link" title="AAA Ssss">AAA Ssss</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yan-jing-58-78" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yan-jing-58-78" class="zg-link" title="严旌">严旌</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ban-zou-50" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ban-zou-50" class="zg-link" title="伴奏">伴奏</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
